name: Prettify 2.1 ( for 2.1!! Inspired in SamDoesArts)
description:
Hello, this is one small experiment i did to prettify the Ugly results i was getting in the 2.1 version.

The images are with and without the Hypernetwork enabled.

It pops up the style the more tags you use.

I trained it with mostly booru tags so you guys know whats up. (Dont expect much)

Look the examples for ideas of the tags.

modelVersions.name: V1
modelVersions.description:
Trained on 41 HD images in 1024.

Uses a wide hypernetwork so it takes a while to get the style to pop up.

Use as many tags as you can!
